<br>
Way I figure mages needs more power anyways <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  because look whose in a group 61 to 65 and look at the classes still kiting and soloing <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  till I can solo PoN and PoD mobs I figure at worse keep everything as is since the majority are happy.<br>
